      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 92,
      "message": "Is there a use case where the existence of tls_info is not enough to indicate that tls should be used?  I'm wondering why a user would have a tls_info object with use_tls equal to False.  Benefit of removing the need for use_tls is that it'll simplify logic in the plugin.",
