    {
      "id": "1a76adc5_a87651a2",
      "file_path": "k8s/k8s-node-type.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 92,
      "message": "My thinking here is that someone developing a component that could be used with TLS would always specify the cert_directory in a blueprint.  use_tls could be provided via an input at deployment time, so that the deployer could decide independently whether to use TLS or not.",
